categories.description:
This will be "Code & Collaboration" if it is one of the following:

1) push;
2) pull_request;
3) pull_request_review;
4) branch_protection_rule

This will be "Project Management" if it is one of the following:  
1) issue;
2) issue_comment;
3) milestone;
4) label

This will be "Repository Life Cycle" if it is one of the following:  
1) fork;
2) repository;
3) public;
4) watch

This will be "Security Operations" if it is one of the following:  
1) secret_scanning_alert;
2) dependabot_alert;
3) workflow_run;
4) deployment
